targets.query: SELECT sum("batch-error") FROM "pipeline_metrics" WHERE ("job_name" = 'TelemetryExtractor') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT sum("batch-error") / (sum("batch-success") + sum("batch-error") + sum("skipped") + sum("duplicate")) * 100 FROM "pipeline_metrics" WHERE ("job_name" = 'TelemetryExtractor') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT sum("error") / (sum("error") + sum("success")) * 100 FROM "pipeline_metrics" WHERE ("job_name" = 'TelemetryLocationUpdater') AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("secondary-route-success") FROM "pipeline_metrics" WHERE ("job_name" = 'TelemetryRouter') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT sum("success") + sum("failed") FROM "pipeline_metrics" WHERE ("job_name" = 'TelemetryValidator') AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("primary-route-success") FROM "pipeline_metrics" WHERE ("job_name" = 'TelemetryRouter') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
